<plot>Salsa and Tango are of course Latino dances. But, in our story they refer to heart and soul of our main characters. Step Papa is Tango, the old traditional kind, arms length. Maria, his step-daughter is Salsa, a mixture of jazz, funk, reggae, hip-hop and samba. These dancers find it impossible to occupy the same space, an explosion is bound to happen. It does when Maria discovers Papa secret.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?475142</url></doc>
